data.description: Short Sale. $10,000 below current appraised value! HECM Short sale. Easy, and quick processing. Accepting FHA Buyers. TOP NOTCH VILLA impeccably upgraded throughout, and move in ready. This clean, well loved home is better than new, and ready for you. Beautiful, easy care, luxury grade vinyl plank floors were installed in 2021. The 8/2022 AC offers you cool comfort through the dog days of Summer. The kitchen is open to the great room, and offers meticulously selected top of the line Bosch stainless steel appliances surrounded by beautifully trimmed cabinets in soothing soft white. The extra storage/office space closet in the breakfast nook combines function, and convenience in an organized space. Custom window treatments complement each room, and offers serenity, and privacy. The extra large back yard is a rare find for Fido. Enjoy the social activities with the neighbors, splash in the community pool, or make a hit on the tennis/pickle ball courts. The convenient location, close to restaurants, grocery stores, and shopping. Conveniently located in Vienna Square, Winter Haven's 55+ community offering the reasonable monthly fee of $355 covering the lawn care, painting, and roof replacement. This 55+ community is an easy choice. Step inside, fall in love. Make it yours!
